| ART-Chat-2.5M | 300,000 | 1483.6 min | **25** | 25 (fanout) | 103 (59.636s, steady) | ✅ YES |
| Mooncake-conversation | 12,031 | 58.9 min | **2** | 2 (fanout) | 4 (57s, steady) | ❌ no |
| Mooncake-toolagent | 23,608 | 58.9 min | **2** | 2 (fanout) | 206 (59.999s, steady) | ❌ no |
